# Copy to .env.local — Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key_here

# ─── Supabase Edge Function secrets (Dashboard → Edge Functions → Secrets) ───
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...     Required for AI Copilot (ai-copilot function)
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=...    Optional; news-feed cache writes use this if set

# ─── No API keys needed for these (free public data via edge functions) ───
# • Stock quotes — Yahoo Finance (market-data function)
# • Mutual fund NAV — AMFI India daily file (market-data function)
# • Financial news — Google News RSS feeds (news-feed function)

# ─── Optional ───
# Google OAuth — configure in Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Providers
